text: KUYO (830 AM) is a Classic Christian format radio station licensed to Evansville, Wyoming. The station can be heard in 14 Wyoming counties,KUYO website and as far away as Salt Lake City during the daytime.Salt Lake City DX report The station signs off at night to protect WCCO in Minneapolis, Minnesota as well as other stations on 830 kHz. ==References== ==External links== UYO Category:Radio stations established in 1985 UYO Category:Natrona County, Wyoming UYO Category:1985 establishments in Wyoming
